entries.femaleVariant: All runnin' away, fast as you can.
Mom, don't talk like that. You know it's not true.
Think I don't got eyes? Can see them streets emptyin' out. Less an' less of the young folks.
Because there's no future for us here. At least there's work in the city, a chance at a decent life.
I'll make some real eddies in Heywood, have you move in with me there. It'll be better for us.
Mm-mm, you tear someone up with their roots, they dry up. My home's here.
Ma, you can't... Ehh, never mind. We'll talk later.
